*Dogodi* se da nismo stigli na vreme. (It happened that we didn't arrive on time.)

*Dogodilo* se da se nismo sreli. (It happened that we didn't meet.)

Kad je *dogodilo* da se sunce vratilo, svi su počeli da slave. (When it happened that the sun returned, everyone started celebrating.)

*Dogodilo* se da je bio veliki sneg. (It happened that there was a lot of snow.)

*Dogodila* se nesreća. (An accident happened.)